&#13;
<h4><p><strong>PeoplePerHour</strong></p></h4>&#13;
&#13;
<p>The PeoplePerHour market allows professionals around the world to find work that suits their qualifications, improving the way sellers communicate with companies while providing them with a variety of tools required by independent tasks.</p>&#13;
&#13;
<p>Displays many features that include proposal presentation, in-app messages, account management, and billing, and pricing plans come in the form of different plans such as monthly, or one-off, payments.</p>&#13;
